          Business question
What impact does healthcare coverage have on cancer deaths prevented?
            Query
SELECT
  coverage,
  ROUND(AVG(deaths_prevented),2)Avg_death
FROM cancer_data
WHERE deaths_prevented > 0
GROUP BY coverage
ORDER BY coverage DESC;

     Insight
This shows that as healthcare coverage increases, more lives are saved.

  Recommendation
There should be an increase in healthcare service,which will help reduce or prevent cancer death
